Requirements to initialize the Pong game:
1. Setting 2 Class P1,P2
2. Each player has a 3 pixel cubes connected to each other
3. Each player can only move up or down.
4. Each player has half of the pixel screen width and height.
5. A crossed line of a turtle object that is set up in the middle of the total screen width and height.
6. A pixel cube which is another turtle object that if it is being hit from each of P side then it returns in the same direction
7. If the pixel cube object hits a wall or the P it returns to that same angel direction. else it its the wall it angels 45 degrees to that same direction.
8. If pixel cube passes the x and y coordinates of the P1 means P2 scored. vice versa.
9. first one to reach certain amount of points wins.